title.40: The Punisher: Die Hard In the Big Easy (1992) #1

description.0: The Silver Surfer swoops in viciously to blindside Doctor Strange! The question is…WHY?
description.4: Crystal and Thor, (aka Eric Masterson), move into the Avengers Mansion. After an emergency call from the Four Freedoms Plaza, the Avengers investigate only to find themselves ensnared in a trap. The return of Swordsman!
description.7: Wonder Man's new movie has a surprising twist! His co-stars are the super villains known as the Night Shift! Iron Man travels to Greenwich Village to seek aid from Doctor Strange in hopes of defeating Stannish!
description.9: What if the Phoenix rose again? When the Phoenix powers are reignited and the Sentinels rise up to destroy all of mutantkind, will the Phoenix be mutantkind's savior or executioner?
description.11: ASSAULT ON ARMOR CITY PART 3. Earth's Mightiest Heroes and Darkhawk guest-star! The Avengers come together to neutralize a threat against Stark Industries that's shaping up to be a full-fledged assault! Plus, a complete dossier on the Golden Avenger's foes.
description.13: Matt Murdock gets a personal victory when his law license is reinstated. Kingpin's back is pressed against the wall, and the authorities are close to an arrest.
description.14: Rachel and Meggan continue trying to restore Meggan's memories by tracking down people from her past, leading them to a nomadic caravan!
description.15: Down in the Florida swamps, Hulk and Rick Jones discover two Man-Things- one good, one evil.
description.16: When the world is in danger of entering a third World War, Tony Stark must risk his life to help stop it! Could this be the beginning of the end for Tony Stark? Guest-starring the Black Widow!
description.18: Eric Masterson tries to jog Donald Blake's memory concerning his alter ego...with disastrous results!
description.19: Eric follows Mephisto to his home dimension to retrieve Mjolnir!
description.21: Strong Guy embraces his destructive side when he takes down "Nasty Boy" Slab in Washington D.C. Who will walk away from the fray? And how much property damage will D.C. suffer?
description.23: The Fantastic Four make it back to Earth, but end up crashing on a deserted island! Things on this island are not as they seem, however, and the team finds themselves under attak by the creature known only as Dreadface!
description.24: When Sunfire discovers a mysterious crater on the Sakhalin Islands, he is knocked out by a mysterious foe. The X-Men arrive soon after, only to be warped into the void that has formed in the crater!
description.25: Logan makes a shocking discovery when he realizes that he was not the only one greatly afflicted by Weapon X!
description.26: The First Appearance of Omega Red!   Just who is this super-powerful mutant named Omega Red...and why does he recognize Wolverine?
description.28: Introducing Marvel's indomitable heroine, the Unbeatable Squirrel Girl! Check out the origin of the Great Lakes Avenger in her first ever appearance!
description.33: Michael Collins’ Deathlok meets Daredevil under surprising circumstances as the Bushwacker targets them both for death!
description.34: Punisher was lost, and now he is found! Nova gets crafty in hijacking the Secret Empire's technology, while Moon Knight and Night Thrasher attack Midnight head-on. The issue that's a collision course set for disaster!
description.35: In the heat of battle against the Secret Empire, Lynn Church pulls an ace out of her sleeve. Will this issue mark the end of Midnight? Spidey and his fellow heroes certainly hope so!
description.36: Cap and Thor (Eric Masterson) are held captive by Doughboy and are scheduled to be killed by nightfall. With no one aware that Cap and Thor are missing, will the two helpless Avengers survive the night? Plus: Rachel Leighton kidnapped!
description.38: She-Hulk comes face-to-face with the Black Talon and his undead gang of monsters!
description.46: Six years after'Return of the Jedi, the'Rebel Alliance'has established a'New Republic'over three-fourths of'the galaxy. The surviving'Imperial'Forces are torn by'civil war'and harassed by rebel attacks. One of these raids ends in disaster: Luke Skywalker'and'Lando Calrissian'are shot down over the former'Imperial City. When news reaches'Han Solo'and Leia Organa, they rush to the rescue, along with'Wookiee'Chewbacca'and'droid'C-3PO, of course!
description.48: After a chemical accident, Spider-Man’s consciousness is separated from his body and he enters an alternate plane where Death herself lies in wait! Not to mention Thanos is there too, in possession of the Infinity Gauntlet!
description.55: Hydra hatches an insidious plot from within Kingpin's ranks. Daredevil edges closer to building a final case on Wilson Fisk.
description.56: Rachel discovers a strange connection between her Phoenix Force and Meggan's lost memories!
description.57: Bruce and Rick Jones learn a devastating secret about their friend Jim Wilson.
description.58: The Dragon Seed Saga epic conclusion! Don't miss out as the real Iron Man dives into the middle of the dragon hordes and begins tearing things up!
description.59: Zarrko pulls out all his time-tripping stops to thwart Beta Ray Bill, Dargo, and Thor II!
description.60: Loki vs. the three incarnations of Thor!
description.62: A man claiming to be the real Jamie Madrox interrupts the team's press conference, and X-Factor springs into action! But who is the real Jamie Madrox? Who is the imposter? A shocking conclusion to an explosive issue!
description.64: Stranded in space! The Fantastic Four have no way to get home light years away, but that's the least of their problems when they have to contend with...Devos the Devastator!
description.65: While Gamesmaster and Selene watch their machinations unfold from afar, the X-Men try to discover the truth about the mutant called Bishop.
description.66: With the help of Jean Grey and Professor X, Wolverine is able to unlock the secrets of his past to reclaim his present.
description.75: Guest-starring Punisher and Moon Knight! Heroes of New York City unite to take down a common enemy in the Secret Empire. With Midnight under close watch, will pertinent answers about the Empire come to light?
description.76: Inner machinations within the Secret Empire leave the whole operation vulnerable. Punisher remains shaken by the heroes' battle with Midnight. With the Empire's highest members struggling for power, will Spider-Man and company exploit a fatal flaw?
description.77: The Sons of the Serpent attack the New Warriors, and the Avengers make it their top priority to uncover their base of operation. Who is the Hate Monger? And why is he perpetuating violence against the team? Plus, a disgraced Avenger is given less-than-two-weeks-notice by Captain America!
description.78: While the Avengers scramble to figure out the Redskull's next move, the Redskull and his Skeleton Crew take some time off for a little R&R. But when Agent Freeman makes a shocking discovery, Steve Rogers' world is rocked!
description.80: Iron Man has a plan to use an escaped villain to lead himself and Living Lighting to three missing Avengers, but when he finds the demon known as Stannish, all plans go out the window!
description.82: What if Phoenix had lived? In one of comics' biggest milestone moments, Jean Grey gave her life to prevent the Phoenix Force from consuming any more worlds. But in a universe where Jean/Phoenix lived on, will the Earth survive against the whims of a cosmic being of purifying flame?
description.86: She-Hulk and Weezi travel to New Orleans to meet with a Voodoo master they believe can help solve a case.
description.89: SILVER SURFER VS. THANOS! Doctor Strange convinces the Surfer to engage in a duel of combat with Thanos in order to crush Nebula's ascension.
description.94: In order to return to his present reality, Silver Surfer must come to terms with his past and forgive himself.
description.97: One of our favorite heroes is finally revived…the Mighty Thor is BACK!
description.99: Matt gets an important dose of intel from Nick Fury that connects Kingpin's television network to Hydra.

0.text: The Silver Surfer swoops in viciously to blindside Doctor Strange! The question is…WHY?

1.text: The Sinister Six attack! It's up to Spidey and Ghost Rider to stop them in their tracks. But they have a new sixth member who may be their most powerful yet!

2.text: The Silver Surfer is brought to the the Collector...and the whole Universe hangs in the balance!

10.text: Quasar must stop a multiversal threat by hopping from reality to reality of universes featured in the pages of What If?. Quasar has saved the galaxy before but can he now save multiple universes?

26.text: The landmark first appearance of Omega Red! Just who is this super-powerful mutant...and why does he recognize Wolverine?

29.text: HOMECOMING CONCLUSION The Guardians collide with the Punishers, Commandeers, and Badoon and Talon!

30.text: SIMILAR MACHINES PART 2 Punisher and Deathlok  chasing a common enemy. Punisher finds that he is short on mercy, while Deathlok struggles to maintain his humanity.

31.text: THE HERO KILLERS PART 3. It's a villain barrage as the mystery figure looking to end Spidey and the New Warriors sends an army of mercenaries after them. Can the heroes withstand the might of Beetle, Blacklash, Boomerang, Constrictor, Hydro-Man, Rhino, Shocker, Speed Demon and more!

32.text: While nursing Arize, the Mojoverse’s Death Sponsors travel to Earth to retrieve him from the X-Men!

37.text: Moon Knight battles against his one-time confidant and long-time foe, Bushman. There's more at stake than just a grudge. Bushman seeks vengeance and will stop at nothing to have it! Bushman brainwashes Frenchie and Marlene into helping him assassinate the world's leaders, and Moon Knight must reluctantly stop his friends at any cost!

38.text: She-Hulk comes face-to-face with the Black Talon and his undead gang of monsters!

39.text: Half-man, half-machine Deathlok is charged with recovering Nick Fury’s Infinity Formula. And if Deathlok should fail…it would spell certain death for Fury! The stakes have never been higher, as Marvel’s mighty cyborg takes on Leviathan for Nick Fury's life!

40.text: Toussaint Murrow has Frank Castle in the palm of his hands. Literally. Meet Mortician in his first EVER appearance!

41.text: Punisher takes on Star Wars-based technology as an advanced group of criminals attempt to flee into space!

42.text: The final showdown between Cap and the Red Skull at last! But even if Cap comes out on top, will he be able to cope with the devastating revelations this victory has brought?

43.text: Frenchie faces off against Killer Shrike and all Moon Knight can do is watch!

44.text: The Warriors try to uncover the Taylor Foundation’s shady activities by interrogating Gideon -- but he comes prepared.

45.text: The Wild One, Shanzar and Lucian Aster, pull out all the stops to defeat Doctor Strange. Thankfully, the Sorcerer Supreme has some backup help from his Defenders friends!

47.text:
Nebula has the Infinity Gauntlet -- and, in the most shocking twist yet,
Thanos now stands with Earth's heroes to defeat her! Can one being
possibly contain all that power? And if not Thanos, then who? With a
shock ending that'll leave you begging for more!

48.text: After a chemical accident, Spider-Man’s consciousness is separated from his body and he enters an alternate plane where Death herself lies in wait! Not to mention Thanos is there too, in possession of the Infinity Gauntlet!

49.text: It's X-Man against X-Man as Magneto's Acolytes brainwash the Children of the Atom for their own amusement.  Will Nick Fury be able to pull out a last minute save?

50.text: The return of the Midnight Sun! Plus some surprising guest stars make an appearance!

51.text: As Dr. Karl Lykos gains control over his alternate persona, The Brotherhood of Mutants captures him and attempts to release Sauron once more.

52.text: Adam Warlock now wears the Infinity Gauntlet and its power is almost too much for him. Doctor Strange gets to use each of his old standby artifacts to counteract the Gauntlet's effects.

53.text: Leviathan steals Nick Fury’s elixir of youth! What is the strange Infinity Formula that has kept Fury young since World War II? And what happens when the years finally catch up to S.H.I.E.L.D.’s top agent? Guest-starring Deathlok!

54.text: In his attempt to claim the sweet prize of Death, Suicide stalks Ghost Rider through the city...

68.text: HOMECOMING PART 3 The Guardians encounter the feral hero called Talon!

69.text: SIMILAR MACHINES PART 1 Deathlok finds that he has more in common with the Punisher than he thinks, when Frank Castle enters a conflict between Deathlok and Silvermaine. Will Deathlok be able to protect his son, embroiled in his own trouble, from Silvermaine’s gang?

70.text: As Cap and Bucky get ever closer to confronting the Red Skull, the mystery identity of the evil Agent X is revealed -- and it shatters the world that Steve Rogers thought he knew forever!

71.text: Moon Knight holds the fate of Hobgoblin in his hands! You won't want to miss this epic crossover with Spider-Man.

72.text: Night Thrasher and Chord have a falling out over the Taylor Foundation's misdeeds -- what does this mean for the New Warriors?

73.text: An Infinity Gauntlet tie-in! The Sleepwalker has his first run-in with the Chain Gang…and it may be his last! Featuring Doctor Strange and Nebula!

74.text: Super-sized special! Each team member goes on a personal mission to dissemble Jonothon Cayre and his Air Walker android. Scattered across the U.K., will Nightcrawler, Meggan, Cap Britain, Shadowcat and Phoenix fare better together…or apart?

86.text: She-Hulk and Weezi travel to New Orleans to meet with a Voodoo master they believe can help solve a case.

89.text: SILVER SURFER VS. THANOS! Doctor Strange convinces the Surfer to engage in a duel of combat with Thanos in order to crush Nebula's ascension.

91.text:
Galactus! The Celestials! The Stranger! Master Order and Lord Chaos! The
all-powerful entities of the universe have united to stand against
Thanos -- and they don't stand a chance! Can the remnants of Earth's
heroes succeed where the gods have failed? And the captive Nebula has
her eyes on that Gauntlet...

92.text: SABOTAGE PART 1 An explosion rocks the World Trade Center. But it's not just an explosion Spidey has to worry about! Warpath and Juggernaut are going head to toe! Can the Wallcrawler help take Juggy down?

93.text: After their assault on Asteroid M, the X-Men stand....defeated?!  Meanwhile, a dark secret from Magneto's past emerges that makes everyone question the depth of his evil.

94.text: In order to return to his present reality, Silver Surfer must come to terms with his past and forgive himself.

95.text: It’s a Cold War all its own, as Wolverine and Nick Fury continue to track Hydra in the Artic wilderness. But when Fury’s mind begins to slip, will Wolverine be able to carry himself, and his teammate, to victory? Insanity plagues Nick Fury, and the timing couldn’t be worse. The battle for the Soviet icebreaker continues!

96.text: SABOTAGE PART 2 It's Warpath, Feral, Shatterstar, and Spider-Man versus the Juggernaut!

97.text: One of our favorite heroes is finally revived…the Mighty Thor is BACK!
